Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡集换卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dirty Bubble trading cards
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上最稀有的集换卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rarest trading cards in existence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(390,806)}肮脏泡泡卡\N真的是用\N肮脏泡泡的脏污做的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要发动先抢先得远古仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I invoke the ancient rite of dibs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真没毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1614,414)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  我的肮脏泡泡收藏集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, my collection of Dirty Bubblobilia
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will finally be complete
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是这里最酷的酷哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the coolest guy here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旧物的灰味最香了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like the smell of vintage dust
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又去逛那家发霉漫画店了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you been in that musty comic shop again?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.37,0:01:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我上楼洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You march yourself upstairs and take your bath
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.25,0:01:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既来之则安之吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While we're here, why not make the most of it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点官方正品肮脏泡泡浴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little official Dirty Bubble bubble bath
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡放哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, where are those cards?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.22,0:02:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还附赠一根肮脏泡泡糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They come with a stick of Dirty Bubble bubble gum
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这股怀旧味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, the nostalgic flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我有些消化不良了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has given me a case of dyspepsia
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你嚼了那个硬皮泡泡糖  解救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You chewing that crusty gum has freed me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我逃出了美人鱼战士的泡泡糖牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from Mermaid Man's bubblegum trap
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字  小胖墩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your name, my bulbous buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新跟班叫这个名字正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a perfect name for my new sidekick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟班当然要跟到我身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or should I say, inside kick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为解救我的回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As a reward for releasing me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是我的同伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're my new partner in crime
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on in--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你比洗澡之前还脏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're even filthier than before you took a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不怪我  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被困在这个肮脏罪犯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped inside this foul felon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不愿意挑拨巨婴跟他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to come between a man child and his mama
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在该脏还得脏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's time to grime
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,肮脏
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摆脱这身黏液可得要大半辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll take forever to get out of this goop
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来办事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, let's get busy now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别附在我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remove yourself from my person
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, fella
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来掩护我犯罪正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you'll be the perfect cover for my crimes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动什么歪点子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't get any funny ideas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡现在可是在支配着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dirty Bubble is in control now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.59,0:03:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,体力活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Physical activity?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事情不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything but that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快做点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, do something
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你知道谁是老大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you know who's boss
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就来肮脏地干一票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's start our grime spree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1254,368)}第一航海银行
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好久都没抢劫过银行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't bagged a bank in ages
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody move
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来熏爆大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a stink up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能得稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We may need to do a little--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗钱一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,money laundering
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,犯罪还真有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess crime does pay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动  肮脏罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze, you filthy felon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢赞美  警官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the compliment, Officer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,污秽
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒有点喜欢上了这场小小的犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to enjoy this little felonious--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,excursion
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过得吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need sustenance, though
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好知道犯什么罪能填饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know the perfect crime to fill our bellies
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢你的胆识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like your moxie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我瞧瞧你的本事  小跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show me what you got, Sidekick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,458)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:33.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1470,454)}艺术
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上把蟹黄堡全都端出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me all your Krabby Patties post haste
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我穿好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your shirt on--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿好黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,goop on
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡全都要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All our Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来服务这位可爱客人  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this charming customer, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上来一份蟹堡全家桶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need a Krabby Bucket, pronto
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好爱你扮的肮脏泡泡  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love the Dirty Bubble cosplay, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.45,0:05:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃了这顿  精神到不能再精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This greasy grub is most invigorating
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来真的是肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The real Dirty Bubble?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚的餐点很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a delightful repast
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.42,0:06:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但恐怕我还是要退钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid I still require a refund
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王  滚出我家蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass, get out of me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但得先把钱还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first, give me me money back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.15,0:06:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我们不会滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we won't be leaving--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先抢个劫再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until we're done thieving
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要在这吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to eat here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我小跟班也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So is my sidekick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再送你一个  同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's another one, partner
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找自个的蟹黄堡吸去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Find your own patty to suck on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.19,0:07:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是美人鱼战士在这就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only Mermaid Man were here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该可以自己应付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we can handle this ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起扎破泡泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go pop that bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop right there, Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这是装成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,致敬美人鱼战士的乐队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Mermaid Man tribute band?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来问候问候海绵战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Mermaid-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小气队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Tightwad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,负能量怪医
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dr. Negative
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有还行蓝孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Affordable Car
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是想说海星男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean "Barnacle Star?"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What he said
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星飞镖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea star swipe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,飞镖
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃我硬币夹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel my penny pinch
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,夹
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心蟹爪  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch the claws, Crabby
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,560)}请洗鳍
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,消毒
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝我的负能量感应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try my negative vibes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,感应
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.32,0:08:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的负能量敌不过我的鄙视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your negativity is no match for my disdain
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,谁理你
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a bummer
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,扫兴
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我们最后的希望了  海星男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're our last hope, Barnacle Star
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我什么招都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I got nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,没有
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,黏糊糊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然打败那些假冒小丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that those counterfeit clowns are pulverized
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来要犯什么滔天大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what nefarious misdeeds should we commit next?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的肮脏力量快用完了  同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My filthy powers are running low, partner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得充能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a recharge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道有个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know the perfect place
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给你补充肮脏力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to invigorate your noxious batteries
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:29.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1438,564)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:38.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,190)}点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给多少桶海霸糊就给多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring out as many buckets of chum as you can
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先出钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show me the money first
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快端上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And keep it coming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然好啊  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, certainly, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,162)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心又好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgustingly delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.65,0:09:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸卖的食物全裤头村最难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket serves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the foulest fare in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能感受到里面的肮脏力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feel its putrid power
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在流经我的泡泡身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coursing through my bubbly body
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,很多桶之后
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要再来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have more
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.64,0:10:26.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,382  383
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:26.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,382, 383--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jackpot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中的还是一大桶海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or should I say chum-pot?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的预判好像出了一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may have made a slight--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,miscalculation
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.84,0:11:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃了这么一大口  我天下无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This chubby chow has made me invincible
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有剩菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leftovers
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是只粉不控制我生活的反派吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll stick to villains who don't control my life
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上回家把澡给我洗完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You come home right this instant and finish your bath
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上来  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right away, Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.09,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFCD&}绵家谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:49.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我出这步  你会如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let's see what you think of this move
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先接一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should get this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yello?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, son
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Patrick and I
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒立跳棋正下得如火如荼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are pretty deep into a game of upside-down checkers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我向来都有时间陪你和老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I always have time for you and Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么说就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're very glad to hear that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们给你准备了个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because we have a surprise for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A surprise?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love surprises
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以马上就过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you come over right away?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you soon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过小蜗可以陪你下完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Gary can finish the game with you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我只剩最后一步棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I only have one move left
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1348,820)}牛油果公寓区\N疗养社区
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿子好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的惊喜一定就在这附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My surprise has to be around here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is, Son
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好看惊喜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就站在上面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're standing on it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识一下你的新弟弟  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meet your new brother, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今早在大门台阶上发现他的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found him on our doorstep this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他超级可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was just as cute as a button
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是我们做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we did
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何正派海绵都会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what any decent sponges would do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就收养了这个弃婴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and immediately adopted the little foundling
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你的新弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your new brother
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都想要一个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted a brother
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你们两个开心玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you two boys have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见俩白痴说的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard the dopes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  老爸老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, "Mommy" and "Daddy"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们变兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're brothers now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟之间无话不谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And brothers tell each other everything
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤其会谈蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially the Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟之间不留秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no secrets between brothers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们得先亲近一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first, we have to get closer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要像亲兄弟一样  一起做事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by doing things together, like brothers do
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先来一局接球游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First up, a little game of catch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这手套太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This glove is too big
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heads up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投得真好  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice throw, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这一球要加点料了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now here comes one with a little spice on it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.96,0:15:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It burns
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Harold
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到两个儿子和睦相处  真是高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's so nice to see our boys getting along
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实高兴  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It really is, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接得也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, enough catch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不现在来分享一下秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about we share secrets now?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.91,0:15:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  兄弟情谊计还没填满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we haven't filled
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our brotherly love meter yet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,366)}秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,828)}兄弟情
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要再多加深一下兄弟情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have more bonding to do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且加深兄弟情最好的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what better way to brotherly bond
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是帮助邻居了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than by helping our neighbors?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋里的善良小姐一定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure these nice ladies will
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会有家务可以给我们做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have some chores for us to do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goody
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们卖的东西我一律不买
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're selling, I'm not buying
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我和我弟在希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My brother and I were hoping
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还剩了一点家务活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you had some housework that needs doing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩看着就像一对怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two look like a couple of weirdos
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不让怪东西碰我家东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I don't let weirdos touch my stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ma
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别理她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind her
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可以修剪我们家海草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You boys can mow our kelp lawn
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,割草机就放在轮胎旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mower's out by the tires
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们向来都很小心  阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're always careful, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弟弟  你来发动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, little brother, you get the motor going
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll drive
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能换个位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we switch places?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可爱了吧  但你太矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's cute, but you're not tall enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没办法控制方向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to work the controls
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使劲拉一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give her a good tug
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要小心才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to be careful
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,修剪得还不错  吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice work, I think
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你们亮晶晶的半毛钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a shiny nickel, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得这么乱还付什么钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're paying for this mess?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别宠他们了  玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit spoiling them, Mary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半毛钱打发谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A lousy nickel?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you decrepit--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.81,0:17:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们发财了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're rich
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来要去垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, next, we're going to head down to the junkyard
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩金属粉碎机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and play with the metal shredder
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经受够你的折磨活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had it with your torturous activities
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.36,0:17:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在小丑学院旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right by the Clown College
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,396)}踩香蕉皮滑倒可恶学校
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须马上走开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get out of here right now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.17,0:17:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕远路回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take the long way home
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会怕小丑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not afraid of clowns, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是早就告诉过你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来了吗  小虾米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not to come around here, Shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该很早就提过了  吱吱哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you might have mentioned that before, Squeakers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我吱吱先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Squeakers to you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.48,0:18:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我的大鞋今天要踩个小痞子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like my big shoes get to stomp a tiny punk today
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brother
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从那个大脚小丑脚下救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you saved me from that big-footed buffoon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟间要互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brothers stick up for each other
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm saying this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.14,0:18:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.26,0:18:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想多陪着你一起做事  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I want to do more stuff with you, big brother
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:01.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,528)}饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,422)}动物园
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵云像大象鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That cloud looks like an elephant fish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵云像刑具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one looks like an iron maiden
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵云像小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one looks like a baby jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵云像深水炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one looks like a depth charge
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我今天这么美好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a truly wonderful day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从小就有很多兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of brothers and sisters growing up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.99,0:19:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是对我好的一个都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but never one who was actually nice to me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弟弟  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little brother, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for what?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在是真兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're real brothers now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好要分享
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to share
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最深最秘密的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my deepest, most secretest secret
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓过绝不告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I swore I'd never tell it to anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能先分享吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you go first?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我哥做啥事都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything for my brother
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之所以外表蛮横
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I put on a gruff exterior
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为不想让世界伤害我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I don't want the world to hurt me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但内心深处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But deep down
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我却害怕会赶跑大家  从此无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'll push everyone away and end up alone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太谢谢你分享了  弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks very much for sharing that, little brother
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然谁都不应该知道的  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one is supposed to know this, but--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.17,0:20:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的领带  是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tie, it's--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a clip-on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来就没学会系领带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never learned how to tie a tie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.44,0:21:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲眼看看我这可憎的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look your eyes upon my accursed shame
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,心里话发泄出来就好受多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure felt good to get that off my chest
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.70,0:21:10.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:10.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你秘密就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's your secret?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  秘密就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, that was it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you upset?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.25,0:21:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're darn right I am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该得把秘密配方告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to tell me the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会有谁理你那个领带
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody cares about your tie
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想听那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to hear?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不能分享
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't share that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都锁我大脑保险箱里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's locked in my brain box
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.73,0:21:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就用这把钥匙开锁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I'll use this key to unlock it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  就怕会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I was afraid of this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.45,0:21:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你俩天生不适合当兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like you two just weren't made to be brothers
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.66,0:21:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such a shame
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.29,0:22:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,负责任的家长唯一会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the only thing responsible parents can do--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让自家的孩子变成别家的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,making our child someone else's problem
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.47,0:22:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜欢有你当弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really liked having you as a brother
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.18,0:22:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就每分每秒都恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I hated every minute--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.31,0:22:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看啊  塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, look, Cecil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a baby boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都想给我们儿子来个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted our son to have a brother
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.16,0:22:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.53,0:22:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来下跳棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's play checkers
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳棋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Checkers
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.79,0:22:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
